<DOC><DOCNO> AP891014-0008 </DOCNO><FILEID>AP-NR-10-14-89 0058EDT</FILEID><FIRST>r i PM-BRF--BuffaloRaces     10-14 0120</FIRST><SECOND>PM-BRF--Buffalo Races,0124</SECOND><HEAD>200 Buffaloes Race in Festival in Thailand</HEAD><HEAD>LaserPhoto BK2</HEAD><DATELINE>BANGKOK, Thailand (AP) </DATELINE><TEXT>   About 200 water buffaloes raced acrossa dirt square and competed in a beauty contest during thetraditional Buffalo Racing Festival.   Hundreds of people watched the festivities in Chonburi Provincenear the capital Friday.   The day began with about 10 groomed buffaloes pulling bright redwooden carts decorated with bananas, coconuts and palm leaves.Their horns were polished and they were adorned with flowers forthe beauty contest.   In a dirt square about the size of a football field, buffaloesraced against buffaloes, then against motorcycles. Their owners wonelectric fans and other prizes.   The festival stems from ancient celebrations honoring thebuffalo.</TEXT></DOC>